title: Introducing: HISTORY This Week
itunes:title: Introducing: HISTORY This Week
itunes:subtitle: This week, something momentous happened. Whether or not it made the textbooks, it most certainly made history. Join HISTORY This Week as we meet the people, visit the places and witness the moments that led us to where we are today.
description:
This week, something momentous happened. Whether or not it made the textbooks, it most certainly made history. Join HISTORY This Week as we turn back the clock to meet the people, visit the places and witness the moments that led us to where we are today.


New episodes every Monday, starting January 2020.


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
